{"tid":1461200,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"睇死你班友仔唔會入機場","createTime":"2019-08-13T06:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T07:17:26.000Z","uid":157454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9b5baf5805c34ba208dc83628e9e2e62cfd7e63b","tid":1461200,"uid":157454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:40:34.000Z","msg":"又話黑警還眼<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>眼呢？</strong></span></span><br />\n政府睇死你班友仔咁撚鍾意翻工唔會再嚟第二日<br />\n睇死你你班友仔會滿足於階段性勝利<br />\n<br />\n尋日可以塞到佢停半日啊<br />\n睇到今日記招林鄭係咁講經濟講機場<br />\n你仲覺得機場冇用咩<br />\n<br />\n爭氣啲啦香港人<br />\n犧牲你幾日翻工時間<br />\n換香港未來唔值得咩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>入嚟機場啊自由閪！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3ab608e10b9252084019d85bc509c39ae2f5a9dd","tid":1461200,"uid":223054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:41:43.000Z","msg":"我係機場留守巴打 我哋會贏！機場係無敵嘅一張牌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1459828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1459828</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ec89a7ccfbde3b811e7fa97947cc90d581a686ed","tid":1461200,"uid":119283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w433epa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw433epa.jpg&h=14cf4fc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">721 811</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">816(攬炒) 818(民陣)</span></span>"}]}